{"tid":585013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清水健自備「勃起飯」便當拍片　裡面有這些菜","createTime":"2018-03-08T09:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T17:06:43.000Z","uid":48083,"like":199,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"7c1c5ae18d20bbc4cfe0752f5888ec484379a2dc","tid":585013,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180308/640_9455f76a7001b6990b61e0b1f90bc653.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180308%2F640_9455f76a7001b6990b61e0b1f90bc653.jpg&h=873c811b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180308/640_f55f72f97c25218adb4fb3d6e7373b7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180308%2F640_f55f72f97c25218adb4fb3d6e7373b7e.jpg&h=4585063e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180308/640_3758e1e77349828175e1d7792e4fce53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180308%2F640_3758e1e77349828175e1d7792e4fce53.jpg&h=c63e831f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本資深AV男優清水健說，入行20年來除了要運動鍛鍊身體以外，飲食也是相當重要的，所以都會準備「勃起飯」便當，讓他帶去拍片現場吃，保持精力。<br />\n<br />\n據《日刊SPA》報導，清水健指出，如果肥胖的話勃起力會下降，「30歲到40歲這段期間勃起力會開始下降，但是比起年齡變大，肥胖的影響會比較大。」清水健說他自己很容易變胖，理由是跟一般上班族一樣，喜歡晚上出去吃東西，像是工作結束以後，會跑去吃燒烤、拉麵等等，所以平時控制飲食外也要注重肌肉鍛鍊，讓兩者取得均衡。<br />\n<br />\n「說起減肥的話，大多數人的想法就是要運動，不過我個人的看法倒是吃飯佔99%，運動僅佔1%而已，對運動消耗的卡路里，以及吃飯攝取的卡路里，這兩著做調整會比較有效率，除了做「大便蹲」鍛鍊外，也要計算蛋白質、碳水化合物、脂肪的攝取量，所以他都會準備「勃起飯」便當拍片的時候吃，「帶去攝影現場的便當，是我的精力跟性慾的泉源」。<br />\n<br />\n至於便當內有那些菜？清水健打開便當，裡面有花椰菜、紅蘿蔔、波菜、高麗菜、小番茄、秋葵、南瓜、甘藍，有時會再加香菇、肌肉香腸、山藥，或者是雞胸肉、切片雞肉。「蔬菜跟香菇有身體必須的維他命、礦物質、食物纖維，雞肉則是高蛋白低脂肪，山藥含有睪酮，都是可以增加勃起力的食材。」<br />\n<br />\n不過清水健也自爆，他並不擅長做料理，所以常常買冷凍食品或是已經切好的蔬菜來煮。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20180308/1310389/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180308%2F1310389%2F&d=E3fy1ovkgYbkuPBlE3JVi54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=69acd901\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180308%2F1310389%2F&h=cb02bb2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20180308/1310389/</a>"},{"pid":"e4bfaa768d92e36ca7fb6b6d226c5e268b7144e6","tid":585013,"uid":61653,"like":129,"dislike":4,"score":125,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0060aa56471937bde49c070cbd9dbf5cd6276f73","tid":585013,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e4bfaa768d92e36ca7fb6b6d226c5e268b7144e6","tid":585013,"uid":61653,"like":129,"dislike":4,"score":125,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e010905295f1e904495a611d4da1e12ec934fd","tid":585013,"uid":28743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cdfa24959f8a52346779dee3980c23244ac0384","tid":585013,"uid":41974,"like":5,"dislike":103,"score":-98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:32:13.000Z","msg":"樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc944bd7994466379206b9ba6d6e9a548c8e2880","tid":585013,"uid":48083,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"quote":{"pid":"8cdfa24959f8a52346779dee3980c23244ac0384","tid":585013,"uid":41974,"like":5,"dislike":103,"score":-98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:32:13.000Z","msg":"樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:34:15.0